Executives & Employees Paths
Holdings & Top Positions



MacroView Investment Management LLC



 OVERVIEW



Date Founded


2010




Headquarters


West Tower, 7315 Wisconsin Avenue, Suite 400, Bethesda, MD 20814-3202




Employees (Worldwide)


3




Industries


Investment Services & Portfolio Management




Company Description


MacroView Investment Management employs an absolute return investment approach in which the allocation of a client's portfolio should be based on the combination of individual risk and return requirements, current risk/reward valuations for each asset class and a solid understanding of the macroeconomic climate. The firm's investment philosophy is anchored in the following time-tested concepts of portfolio management theory along with common sense: (1) Tactical Asset Class Rotation and Diversification: (2) Top-Down Macro Analysis and (3) Comprehensive Trading Strategies. MacroView Investment may use many types of trade executions to most effectively execute their strategies. In addition to the outright purchase of securities, the firm also utilizes inverse equity strategies and long/short pairings. The accounts they manage may invest in the following types of securities: exchange-listed securities, securities traded over-the-counter, foreign issues, corporate debt securities (other than commercial paper), commercial paper, certificates of deposit, municipal securities, mutual fund shares and US government securities.




Website


http://www.macroviewim.com





