May 09, 2017
            - Macroview Investment Management Llc has filed a 13F-HR form disclosing ownership of 100
            shares of Vuzix Corp (NASDAQ:VUZI)
            .
        
Other investors with positions similar to Macroview Investment Management Llc include
                Ladenburg Thalmann Financial Services Inc, Bank Of America Corp /de/ , IFP Advisors, Inc, Barclays Plc , Thompson Davis & Co., Inc.,  and Raymond James & Associates.
            
Vuzix Corp has declared a standard industrial code (sic) of 3663 which
        is the "Radio and Television Broadcasting and Communications Equipment" industry.
        
            Macroview Investment Management Llc's top industries are
             
                 "Food And Kindred Products" (sic 20), 
                 "Printing, Publishing, And Allied Industries" (sic 27),  and 
                 "Depository Institutions" (sic 60).
        
        

