•   BETHESDA, MD
                          • Investment Advisor
                      
How do I update this listing?




                                             Macroview Investment Management is based out of Bethesda. Macroview Investment Management is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $92,822,987 (Form ADV from 2017-03-23).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $17,360,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 80.46%. Macroview Investment Management's largest holding is SPDR S&P 500 ETF Index Depositary Receipts with shares held of 14,543.   WhaleWisdom has at least 22 13F filings in our database for Macroview Investment Management. 
                                           














